---
title: Tokhi Bombs
hidden: false
---
The&nbsp;**Tokhi Bombs**&nbsp;is a strategy used in&nbsp;[The Bed of Chaos](https://darksouls.wikidot.com/the-bed-of-chaos)&nbsp;bossfight. It was discovered by the runner&nbsp;[tokhi_join](https://twitch.tv/tokhi_join)&nbsp;and is commonly used in speedruns since December 2013. It saves about 1:10 minutes.

