- Bow Tutorial [https://youtu.be/irkNhIIMjKA](https://youtu.be/irkNhIIMjKA) by Regole on YouTube.
- Very Quick execution [https://youtu.be/Z0cx7wCTqsw?list=PLgswmMvZsZ1UmUU_DYlzIMaSyqDYOv57r](https://youtu.be/Z0cx7wCTqsw?list=PLgswmMvZsZ1UmUU_DYlzIMaSyqDYOv57r) by aeiou on Youtube
- Bowless Tutorial [https://youtu.be/eTxrzaJsAsQ](https://youtu.be/eTxrzaJsAsQ) by San on YouTube.
